[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "さて、あれから１週間が経過したわけだが……\nイェルカたちはちゃんと言いつけを守ったかな？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_00561",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "もし、してなかったら……\nその……やっぱり？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_036_00562",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "うむ、そのときは我らが「管理」をしてやるまでじゃ。\n戦いになるじゃろうなぁ、うずうずするわい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_036_00563",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "ふっ、この１週間、そこらへんを見て回ったが\nなかなか楽しかったな。退屈しなかった",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_00564",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "久方ぶりの世界は面白いものがたくさんじゃ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_036_00565",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "特にあのホルハーツなる島。\n妙な催しが多くて実に愉快な島じゃった",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_036_00566",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "ああ、時間があっという間に感じたほどだ。\nこの俺の上機嫌、損ねてほしくはないものだな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_00567",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "姉貴たち……大丈夫、だよね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_036_00568",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "キューン、何か言ったか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_00569",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "あっ！　な、なんでもない、よ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_036_00570",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "お待たせ。待った？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00571",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "長兄として、少し待つぐらいはしてやるさ。\nそれで、どうなんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_00572",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "このヘルト様の命令通り、\n不穏分子の「管理」を遂行したんだろうな？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_00573",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "してない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00574",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "……なんだと？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_00575",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "あんたの指示には従えない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00576",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "うぬら、まさかそんな世迷言を抜かすだけで\nこの１週間を無為に過ごしたとでもいうのか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_036_00577",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "ま、ままま、まずいって……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_036_00578",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "一方的すぎる要求は聞けないわ。\n私はあんたたちに問いかけにきたの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00579",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "その準備を１週間かけてしてきたのよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00580",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "ほう、準備？　興味深い単語が出てきたじゃないか。\nなんの準備だ？　話してみろよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_00581",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "一度気になると答えが出るまで食らいつく……\nやっぱりアタシの知ってるヘル兄だね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00582",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "あんたたち二人、目覚めたばかりだしさ。\n当座の目標としてアウグストの指示に従うのは分かる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00583",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "でも、二人はアウグストたちに\n絶対服従しているわけじゃないでしょ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00584",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "当たり前だ。親ではあるが、この俺が\n無理にまで命令を聞いてやる道理はない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_00585",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "じゃあクリセルダたちを「管理」しろって命令も\n聞かないでほしいんだけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00586",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "目覚めた時に聞いた話では、\n始末されても当然のことをした連中だと思うが？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_00587",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "でも今を生きている人たちはその必要はないって\n判断してるのよ、私もそう思う",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00588",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "だからね、聞きかじった話だけで判断するんじゃなくて\nもっと色んなことを知ってから判断してほしいの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00589",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "できれば今の時代、もうパルメ族の「管理」は\n必要ないってところまで判断が出てくれると最高ね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00590",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "パルメ族の判断じゃない、\nヘルト、ゼロとしての判断で！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00591",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "アウグストではなく、俺個人としての判断か。\nなるほどな。よく考えたじゃないか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_00592",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "今のところ、上手くいってるね。\n確かに対話しようっていうより、いい切り口だったかも",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00593",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "とにかく、自我の強いところを突いて、\n気まぐれを起こさせる……まぁ悪くないと思うよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00594",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "もっとも、気まぐれすぎて、この一瞬後には\n急に怒りだしている可能性もあるけどね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00595",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "「管理」を思い留まってほしい理由は分かった。\nそれは、人間から頼まれてのことか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_00596",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ううん。レスナたちに頼まれたわけじゃない。\n私がそうしたい……そうしなきゃって思ったの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00597",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "……なるほど、すっかり変わったじゃないか。\n昔のお前は……ナナは力で解決するのが得意だった",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_00598",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "そういうところを我は気に入っておったのじゃが。\nすっかり丸くなりおって……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_036_00599",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "とにかく今の世界は、人間同士の管理で上手いこと\n回っているの。まだ起きたばかりだから知らないでしょ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00600",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 40,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "図書の島に愛の島、演劇の島……この諸島だけでも\n色んな文化の、しかも平和的な島がたくさんある",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00601",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 41,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "愛の島はもう知っとる。この１週間で見たのじゃ。\n確かに愉快じゃったな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_036_00602",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 42,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "なら、私の言いたいことも分かるでしょ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00603",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 43,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ランターナ大陸だってある……まだ見てない世界が\nたくさんあるんだから、もっと見てきたらどう？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00604",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 44,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "うむ……諸島のほうはいくつか島を回ったが、\nランターナ大陸の方面はまだ回っていないな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_00605",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 45,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "それぞれの土地にそれぞれの文化、風習がある。\nとにかく、世界は広くて、多様なのよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00606",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 46,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "それぞれの土地の者に管理を任せたほうが良いと\n言いたいわけか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_036_00607",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 47,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "さすがゼロお姉さま、話が分かる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00608",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 48,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "まぁのぉ、察しは結構良いのじゃ、はっはっは！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_036_00609",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 49,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（これはいい流れだ。畳みかけるしかない！）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00610",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 50,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "そうそう。闘技場のある島なんてのもあるんだよ。\nゼロ姉、そういうの好きでしょ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00611",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 51,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "うむ、それは面白そうじゃな！\n",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_036_00612",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 52,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "下手したら、そういう面白いものを見る前に\n潰しちゃうかもしれないんだよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00613",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 53,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "二人が眠ってから変わった世界のこと、\n知ってみるのも悪くないんじゃないかい？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00614",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 54,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "……なるほど、お前たちの言葉も\nあながち間違っていないと感じる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_00615",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 55,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "昔はともかく、今の世界がどうなっているか\n俺とゼロはまだ断片的にしか知らない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_00616",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 56,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "お前たちがそこまで言うなら、アウグストの言葉を\n鵜呑みにするのは、英雄として違うな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_00617",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 57,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "じゃあ……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00618",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 58,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "だが、このまま去るのもな、どうもお前たちに\n丸め込まれたような感じで、気に入らない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_00619",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 59,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "力を試すついでだ、ゼロ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_00620",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 60,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "人の力でどれほどの障害を乗り越えることが\nできるのか……力を見せてもらおうかのう！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_036_00621",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 61,
		"localized_name": "ドラゴン",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ガオオオォォンン！！！！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 62,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "ど、ドラゴン……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_036_00623",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 63,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "こいつを置いていく。パルメ族の「管理」が\n必要ないというなら、最低限の力は見せろよ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_00624",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 64,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "さあ、ゆくぞキューン",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_036_00625",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 65,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "俺たちが世界を見ている間、お前とヤドヴィガには\n通常通り、パルメの役目をこなしといてもらおう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_00626",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 66,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "う、うん……みんな、その、頑張ってね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_036_00627",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 67,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "くっ……結局こうなるってこと？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00628",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 68,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "なに言ってるのさ、大成功じゃないか。\nあの二人を相手するよりよっぽど楽だよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00629",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 69,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ドラゴンが格下ってほうが、よっぽどでしょ……\nまあ、あの海の光景よりいくらかマシか……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00630",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 70,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "みんな、勝とう！　ヴァレリアたちが生み出してくれた\nこの好機、絶対に掴み取ろう！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00631",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]